{"title_page": "Phases (Alma and French Montana song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name     = Phases\n| cover    =\n| alt      =\n| type     = single\n| artist   = [[Alma (Finnish singer)|Alma]] & [[French Montana]]\n| album    =\n| released = {{Start date|2017|09|21}}\n| format   = \n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded =\n| studio   =\n| venue    =\n| genre    =\n| length   =\n| label    =\n| composer =\n| lyricist =\n| producer =\n}}\n\n'''''Phases''''' is a song by Finnish singer Alma and American rapper [[French Montana]]. The song was written by Alma, [[Charli XCX]], [[French Montana]], Noonie Bao, and Sasha Sloan and produced by Charlie Handsome, Rex Kudo and Styalz Fuego. The song was released as a single on through PME Records on September 21, 2017.<ref name=\"p\"/> The musc video for the single was directed by [[Charli XCX]].<ref>{{cite web |last1=Williams |first1=Nick |title=Glow-In-The-Dark Finnish Pop Star ALMA On Global Breakthrough, Famed Neon Locks, & Working With BFF Charli XCX |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/lifestyle/8023160/finland-pop-star-alma-charli-xcx-french-montana-interview-new-face-fresh-style |website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |date=2017-11-04|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n==Background==\nAlma released her debut extended play ''Dye My Hair'' in 2016. In 2017, she was featured on [[Sub Focus]]' single \"Don't You Feel It\" and [[Martin Solveig]]'s single \"[[All Stars (song)|All Stars]]\". \"Phases\" was released following Alma's successful solo single \"[[Chasing Highs]]\". Alma spoke of the song's recording process with [[Charli XCX]], saying \"We finished the song in Finland and it was very nice for us to hang out there and finish the whole track there. It\u2019s just about teenage phases. When you\u2019re getting drunk Friday and think you like someone, Saturday you wake up like \u201cno\u201d and sometimes you hurt someone else\u2019s feelings\".<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kent |first1=Matthew |title=ALMA talks French Montana-collab: \u201cHe was so nice!\u201d |url=https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/latest-news/alma-talks-french-montana-collaboration-phases |website=The Line of Best Fit |accessdate=2020-04-10 |date=2017-09-22}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref name=\"p\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/phases-single/1281639252|title=Phases - Single by ALMA & French Montana|publisher=[[iTunes]] (UK)|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n| title1  = Phases\n| length1 = 3:23\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/phases-autograf-remix/1445124493?i=1445124495|title=Phases (Autograf Remix)- Single by ALMA & French Montana|publisher=[[iTunes]] (UK)|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n| title1  = Phases\n|note1 = Autograf Remix\n| length1 = 3:42\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/phases-kda-remix-single/1444851477|title=Phases (KDA Remix)- Single by ALMA & French Montana|publisher=[[iTunes]] (UK)|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n| title1  = Phases\n|note1 = KDA Remix\n| length1 = 3:32\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/phases-acoustic-version-single/1444622071|title=Phases (Acoustic Version)- Single by ALMA |publisher=[[iTunes]] (UK)|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n| title1  = Phases\n|note1 = Acoustic version\n| length1 = 3:33\n}}\n\n\n== Charts ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2017)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Finland|14|artist=French Montana, Alma|song=Phases|rowheader=true|accessdate=2020-04-10}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Heatseeker Singles ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4403|title=NZ Heatseeker Singles Ch